I found these while looking thru my old insta posts, and im reposting because i think a few people dont know the original version of ITGR was in black and white and was very sketchy. 

Both of these arts are SUPER old now tho... jfc the black and white ones are like 2.5 years old?? 

We're waaayayayayayay beyond where the original left off (about chapter 16) so theres no 1:1 panels i can use to compare now...
